		<title>MiCA Decoded: Offshore Corporate Structures With MiCA Licensing: What Nobody Thought Possible</title>
		<link>https://news.bitcoin.com/mica-decoded-offshore-corporate-structures-with-mica-licensing-what-nobody-thought-possible/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Guest Author]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 09:30:12 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Legal]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Compliance]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[legal]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[LegalBison]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[MiCA]]></category>
